These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: orange, purple, azure, grey, red, coral, pink
The people have 7 different jobs:  software-developer, videographer, project-manager, firefighter, social-worker, writer, librarian
House: palace, tower, futuristic, cape-cod, wooden, cottage, modern
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, cooking, dancing, traveling, woodworking, chess
 1. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
 2. the wooden house is the firefighter##1
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the futuristic house##1
 4. the videographer is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 5. the software-developer is on the right of the librarian##1
 6. the person who likes purple is the futuristic house##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the social-worker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is chess and the writer##2
 9. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
10. the person who likes azure is in the middle##1
11. the palace house is the person who likes red##1
12. the person who likes red is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person who likes orange is on the left of the project-manager##1
14. the writer is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
15. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the librarian##1
16. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
17. the cottage house is on the left of the project-manager##1
18. the person who likes pink is on the right of the social-worker##1
19. the modern house is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Color      | purple  | coral        | red | azure      | grey     | orange      | pink     |
| Job   | videographer | firefighter         | librarian   | software-developer | writer    | social-worker | project-manager |
| House         | futuristic | wooden | palace | tower | modern  | cottage  | cape-cod    |
| Hobby     | traveling  | woodworking         | writing     | magic-tricks    | cooking | dancing     | chess     |

